rComments: Prof David is a very caring individual, he has a way of making students feel welcome and offers help and advice when needed. He has a tremendous amount of experience in sculpture and is always helping to guide artists to their true potential. Very sweet, kind and funny.

Took for sculpture and the body. Sculpture is a really hard medium to work with and very time consuming. He is very flexible with his deadline, gave us an extra 3 weeks for our first project. Very nice and always willing to help, since he is the sculpture tech he is there everyday to help you if you need it. Great class, hardly went and did well.

really quiet and shy. He'll answer a question if you ask but not the most helpful. projects are interesting but it would have been nice to explore more materials. Always make your sculpture simpler than you think you need to.
Really inspiring artist and instructor - helped me figure out my concept and how to enhance my skills... VERY helpful and SEXY I can't stop staring at him in class!
